<class module="videoDriver" runtimeProfile="wb" qualifiedName="com.tridium.videoDriver.ui.camera.BVideoPtzBinding" name="BVideoPtzBinding" packageName="com.tridium.videoDriver.ui.camera" public="true">
<description>
Instances of this class act as the glue between a pan/tilt/zoom widget and a station-side&#xa; camera component. Instances of this class invoke corresponding station-side actions on&#xa; station-side components that are bound to client-side widgets.&#xa; &#xa; More specifically, this class invokes the &#x27;move&#x27; and/or &#x27;zoom&#x27; actions on station-side&#xa; camera components (where video driver, field-bus communications occurs) in response to&#xa; a video user, from a user interface, requesting that a camera either pan, tilt, or zoom.
</description>
